General.Name: Arcoma AB
General.Description: Arcoma AB develops, produces, and provides radiology solutions worldwide. It offers digital x-ray systems for radiographic applications, as well as for use in general, eneral, muscle/skeleton, thoratic, pediatric, and trauma/resus clinics. The company sells its products through OEM partners. Arcoma AB was incorporated in 1990 and is based in Växjö, Sweden.
